{"sections":{"6bad968a-7a95-4c72-b78c-cbfa9be9fe61":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__6bad968a-7a95-4c72-b78c-cbfa9be9fe61-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/xay-dung-content-pillar.png","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":1,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__6bad968a-7a95-4c72-b78c-cbfa9be9fe61-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":50,"max_columns":1,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":true,"padding_top":32,"padding_bottom":28,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"1653d525-6a84-4812-80ba-23b8cac785c9":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__1653d525-6a84-4812-80ba-23b8cac785c9-heading-1":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Ready-to-Use Pillar Page Template for Immediate Implementation","heading_size":100}},"template--20671548883249__1653d525-6a84-4812-80ba-23b8cac785c9-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Creating pillar pages is the best way to organize your website content and develop an ultimate guide with multiple pieces of content targeting related keywords that don't cannibalize each other. <br\/><br\/>It is an effective way of improving the user experience of your website and increasing organic traffic.<br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__1653d525-6a84-4812-80ba-23b8cac785c9-heading-1","template--20671548883249__1653d525-6a84-4812-80ba-23b8cac785c9-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"#ffffff","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507":{"type":"newsletter","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507-heading-1":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Download the free pillar page template for your use ","heading_size":70}},"template--20671548883249__8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507-paragraph-1":{"type":"paragraph","settings":{"text":"<p>Please check your inbox for an email from us containing the download link. If you don't see it, kindly check your spam folder.<\/p>"}},"template--20671548883249__8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507-email_form-1":{"type":"email_form","settings":{"button_label":"Download"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507-heading-1","template--20671548883249__8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507-paragraph-1","template--20671548883249__8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507-email_form-1"],"settings":{"background_color_light":"#8cd1ff","background_color_dark":"","padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"1692691734db5509f4":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":false}},"634cb14b-5dc6-49c1-ac61-1beb070f02a7":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"c513958c-0b9b-4ceb-8e82-ccdcc725ce6d":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"How To Use The  Pillar Page Template","heading_size":100}},"template--20671548883249__634cb14b-5dc6-49c1-ac61-1beb070f02a7-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Build topic cluster strategy <\/h3><p>Topic clusters are a group of related content topics on which you will create your pillar page and cluster blogs. It is important that you create a comprehensive topic cluster to cover all the aspects of your broad topic and answer all the questions of the reader. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["c513958c-0b9b-4ceb-8e82-ccdcc725ce6d","template--20671548883249__634cb14b-5dc6-49c1-ac61-1beb070f02a7-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"#ffffff","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":0}},"454ae8d1-27a5-43ab-acc3-b248166930d8":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__454ae8d1-27a5-43ab-acc3-b248166930d8-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8da49340a703035567c0_ppt_1.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":5,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__454ae8d1-27a5-43ab-acc3-b248166930d8-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":3,"height_desktop":300,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"03f41353-3005-42cf-a193-ffce7caae036":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__03f41353-3005-42cf-a193-ffce7caae036-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>To create a topic cluster, start by identifying related keywords for your broad topic. You will see the different ways people are searching for information. For example, in the above image, the topic cluster for ‘planning a family trip’ contains sub-topics like travel planner, trip budget, packing, and places to visit. <\/p>"}},"d032d72c-cbf7-4029-914d-a2be37fb053e":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Content outline template <\/h3><p>The second step is to create a content outline for all the topics in your cluster. From the pillar page to the last subtopic blog, every piece of content should have a defined outline. This exercise will ensure content quality and identify easy opportunities for hyperlinks right at the start. <\/p><p>To create a content outline, start by listing the main points you want to cover in the piece. Club those points based on relevance and create working headings for each section. Remember, your heading should be keyword-loaded for maximum impact. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__03f41353-3005-42cf-a193-ffce7caae036-text-1","d032d72c-cbf7-4029-914d-a2be37fb053e"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"#ffffff","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"798a5822-67ee-4045-83d7-d8e07bec775d":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__798a5822-67ee-4045-83d7-d8e07bec775d-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8db1f668733c77c9af78_ppt_2.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":6,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__798a5822-67ee-4045-83d7-d8e07bec775d-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":1,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"8b741f2a-3249-49d2-b17b-209d01110f96":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__8b741f2a-3249-49d2-b17b-209d01110f96-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>For instance, in the image above, you can see the content outline for this very blog, how it highlights all the important points to be discussed and defines the flow of information for the piece.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__8b741f2a-3249-49d2-b17b-209d01110f96-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"#ffffff","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"06f21ca5-4a09-49ee-8c06-f70da6782c05":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__06f21ca5-4a09-49ee-8c06-f70da6782c05-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>SERP analysis <\/h3><p>SERP analysis is the most important part of creating a pillar page because it involves inspecting the top-ranking competitors for your broad term. While analyzing a web page from a SERP, look at the basic metrics such as PA (page authority) and DA (domain authority). You can use a free tool like Mozbar to do this.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__06f21ca5-4a09-49ee-8c06-f70da6782c05-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"#ffffff","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"69018a26-c607-437e-a742-170b819f6c47":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"d7a5c8be-e33f-40d0-9cfa-048f060dca1c":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8dba9340a70303556d47_ppt_3.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":6,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["d7a5c8be-e33f-40d0-9cfa-048f060dca1c"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":6,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"29ddafef-1b5a-46ee-be5a-ab130eeafc9f":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__29ddafef-1b5a-46ee-be5a-ab130eeafc9f-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Internal links with anchor text<\/h3><p>The goal of every pillar page is to create a comprehensive linking structure where you can help visitors get in-depth information on every topic related to your company. It is important you use the same anchor text everywhere you link to a cluster blog. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__29ddafef-1b5a-46ee-be5a-ab130eeafc9f-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"#ffffff","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"b3714f93-eb55-4ae7-a5a8-93e4e532b53d":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__b3714f93-eb55-4ae7-a5a8-93e4e532b53d-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8dc89340a7030355772d_ppt_4.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":6,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__b3714f93-eb55-4ae7-a5a8-93e4e532b53d-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":6,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"c3cf9732-1914-4988-9c49-8a443694da26":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__c3cf9732-1914-4988-9c49-8a443694da26-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Citations and references<\/h3><p>Citations and references help the visitor verify the facts and statistics in your content and increase the credibility of your content. While researching for your pillar page content, you will find many amazing statistics you could integrate into your content. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__c3cf9732-1914-4988-9c49-8a443694da26-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":0}},"7a09919b-05a0-49a7-bb39-a37f0e7c1486":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__7a09919b-05a0-49a7-bb39-a37f0e7c1486-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8dc89340a7030355772d_ppt_4.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":6,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__7a09919b-05a0-49a7-bb39-a37f0e7c1486-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":6,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"729a2dcb-fa52-4458-9300-5fa762cf32c9":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__729a2dcb-fa52-4458-9300-5fa762cf32c9-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Creating a list of citations and references will help you use them later during the content creation process. In this step, you should list all the sources of information, mention the intriguing fact or statistic, and keep a link to the page for future reference.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__729a2dcb-fa52-4458-9300-5fa762cf32c9-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":28}},"0d5b985f-5ba4-4b90-aed0-88e2830701a2":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__0d5b985f-5ba4-4b90-aed0-88e2830701a2-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>FAQs <\/h3><p>FAQs have become an integral part of blogs. Website visitors are often short of time, and they love skimming through content and reading the FAQs to decide whether they should read the blog in detail or not. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__0d5b985f-5ba4-4b90-aed0-88e2830701a2-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":0}},"7a4185f4-f78d-4c49-b29b-2bc9a4c4b887":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__7a4185f4-f78d-4c49-b29b-2bc9a4c4b887-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8ddb9340a70303557e13_ppt_6.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":6,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__7a4185f4-f78d-4c49-b29b-2bc9a4c4b887-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":6,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"a36373bd-54d0-4dc1-afac-a40646bba0d1":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__a36373bd-54d0-4dc1-afac-a40646bba0d1-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Create a list of popular FAQs related to your topic. You can find FAQ inspiration from competitor blogs or the ‘People Also Ask’ section of Google SERPs. Community forums like Quora, Reddit, and Discord are also great sources for identifying FAQs<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__a36373bd-54d0-4dc1-afac-a40646bba0d1-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":0}},"b1ef0aea-5969-4c06-b28d-9bc1eafd1036":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__b1ef0aea-5969-4c06-b28d-9bc1eafd1036-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>CTA <\/h3><p>CTAs are tricky. It is important to have a ready reckoner of different angles from which you can pitch your product or services. Put on your creative hat and list the ways in which you can link to your product page or services section. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__b1ef0aea-5969-4c06-b28d-9bc1eafd1036-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":20,"padding_bottom":0}},"cc0a2597-f621-4e09-af17-e764373e86be":{"type":"media-gallery","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__cc0a2597-f621-4e09-af17-e764373e86be-media-1":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/647b8def24d3836c8d1ed2d5_ppt_7.webp","image_link":"","overlay_opacity":0,"video_url":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"video_alt_text":"","number_of_columns":6,"number_of_row":1,"title":"","title_size":80,"text":"","text_align":"center","button_label":"","button_link":"","text_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__cc0a2597-f621-4e09-af17-e764373e86be-media-1"],"settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":100,"max_columns":6,"height_desktop":500,"show_section_divider":false,"full_width":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":28,"min_columns_mobile":"1","height_mobile":200}},"e055e09b-4ef6-4124-8edd-0f8feea482ac":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__e055e09b-4ef6-4124-8edd-0f8feea482ac-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Try and address the problem with your CTAs. If you are sure about the placement of the CTAs, you can add a column for ‘CTA Location’ for future reference. <\/p><p>Remember, the goal is to create a central repository of information that addresses all the concerns of the reader. Focus on the readability of your content. Make sure visitors find useful information when they click on hyperlinks in your subtopic blog post.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__e055e09b-4ef6-4124-8edd-0f8feea482ac-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","background_color_light":"","background_color_dark":"","content_alignment":"center","show_section_divider":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":28}},"3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54":{"type":"newsletter","blocks":{"template--20671548883249__3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54-heading-1":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Download the free pillar page template for your use ","heading_size":100}},"template--20671548883249__3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54-paragraph-1":{"type":"paragraph","settings":{"text":"<p>By now, we hope you have a fair understanding of what must be done to create an awesome pillar page. <\/p><p>You can download the free pillar page template for future reference here.<\/p>"}},"template--20671548883249__3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54-email_form-1":{"type":"email_form","settings":{"button_label":"Download"}}},"block_order":["template--20671548883249__3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54-heading-1","template--20671548883249__3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54-paragraph-1","template--20671548883249__3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54-email_form-1"],"settings":{"background_color_light":"#e9e9e9","background_color_dark":"","padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}}},"order":["6bad968a-7a95-4c72-b78c-cbfa9be9fe61","main","1653d525-6a84-4812-80ba-23b8cac785c9","8c5bce3a-a130-42ea-a235-801943ec9507","1692691734db5509f4","634cb14b-5dc6-49c1-ac61-1beb070f02a7","454ae8d1-27a5-43ab-acc3-b248166930d8","03f41353-3005-42cf-a193-ffce7caae036","798a5822-67ee-4045-83d7-d8e07bec775d","8b741f2a-3249-49d2-b17b-209d01110f96","06f21ca5-4a09-49ee-8c06-f70da6782c05","69018a26-c607-437e-a742-170b819f6c47","29ddafef-1b5a-46ee-be5a-ab130eeafc9f","b3714f93-eb55-4ae7-a5a8-93e4e532b53d","c3cf9732-1914-4988-9c49-8a443694da26","7a09919b-05a0-49a7-bb39-a37f0e7c1486","729a2dcb-fa52-4458-9300-5fa762cf32c9","0d5b985f-5ba4-4b90-aed0-88e2830701a2","7a4185f4-f78d-4c49-b29b-2bc9a4c4b887","a36373bd-54d0-4dc1-afac-a40646bba0d1","b1ef0aea-5969-4c06-b28d-9bc1eafd1036","cc0a2597-f621-4e09-af17-e764373e86be","e055e09b-4ef6-4124-8edd-0f8feea482ac","3cdf1ce3-93b1-4b1b-9ff7-fca92ad41f54"]}